# ── IP Whitelist for Admin Routes ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated list of allowed IPs for admin access.
# Supports exact IPs and CIDR notation (e.g., 192.168.1.0/24).
# If empty or not set, all IPs are allowed (development mode).
# Example: ADMIN_ALLOWED_IPS=127.0.0.1,192.168.1.0/24
# ADMIN_ALLOWED_IPS=127.0.0.1,192.168.1.0/24
